Description:
This version of operating system is based on Windows 7 Professional SP1 64-Bit and created by Nishant and is specially made for people who are in the field of business and need the applications to run smoothly and effectively. The system registry is optimized to maximum level. New default theme, New logon screen, New high quality icons, New HQ wallpapers, New sample music, New useful additional gadgets. In normal Windows 7 you don't have Dreamscene enabled, But enjoy using Dreamscene in this version of Windows 7. Removed old ATI, NVIDIA and Intel Graphics Card Drivers and updated to the latest. Updated DirectX files up-to-date. It will be more comfortable, faster and reliable than other windows 7 professional operating systems. All the critical errors which the users faced in Windows 7 Professional are fixed in this version of operating system. Enjoy using Windows 7 Regal Business Edition 2014 64-Bit from Reckons International Team!!!

Release Overview
Platform: AMD64 / Windows
Created By: Nishant (Reckons International Team)
Released Date: 15.07.2013
Version: Based On: Windows 7 Professional
Architecture: 64-Bit
